re more dedication and effort than ever before.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]","streaming":[{"name":"HIDIVE","url":"https://www.hidive.com/season/19080"},{"name":"iQ","url":"https://www.iq.com/album/elud8qa5ah"}],"type":"TV","genres":["Sports"]},{"id":52031,"title":"Itou Junji: Maniac","title_english":"Junji Ito Maniac: Japanese Tales of the Macabre","episodes":12,"score":6.69,"start_date":"2023-01-19T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":null,"image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1956/132879l.jpg","synopsis":"The anime series will adapt 20 stories from a number of Itou's manga for the first time, including Tomie, Souichi, and Kubitsuri Kikyuu (The Hanging Balloons).\n\n(Source: MAL News)","streaming":[{"name":"Netflix","url":"https://www.netflix.com/title/81295011"}],"type":"ONA","genres":["Drama","Horror","Supernatural"]},{"id":50864,"title":"Ooyukiumi no Kaina","title_english":"Kaina of the Great Snow Sea","episodes":11,"score":6.69,"start_date":"2023-01-12T00:00:00+00:00","end_date":"2023-03-23T00:00:00+00:00","image":"https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1064/131833l.jpg","synopsis":"Humanity is facing extinction. In a snow-covered world where water has become scarce, the last habitable lands are located at the feet of gigantic Orbital Trees scattered about the desolated Earth. According to a legend, there exists a sage who knows the secret to producing abundant quantities of water to save mankind. \n\nRiriha, the princess of Atland, uses an organic hot-air balloon to climb to the top of an Orbital Tree in hopes of meeting her country's savior. Once she reaches the Canopy—an area that appears to be an infinite window of transparent ice—she meets Kaina, one of the last men alive on the Canopy. However, she can not find the man she was looking for.\n\nUnable to return by herself to her country, the princess finds a helping hand in Kaina, who is eager to explore the surface world that he thought was empty. As Kaina learns about the war against Ririha's country,